						               													<description>In MadSoccer, every player will be responsible for their own national football team, making sure to tactically defeat the opponents. Everyone has action cards (including attack, defence, penalties, etc.) with different characteristics, and has to properly and thoughtfully use them in order to win. For the game to end, the participants have to manage resources and eliminate the defenders, midfielders and strikers of the rival teams.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;How To Play:&amp;#10;&amp;#10;     Choose your favourite football team! (Netherlands, Belgium, Spain, France, Germany, Portugal, Turkey, and England)&amp;#10;     Put your players in the right place and take out all opponents!&amp;#10;     First, defeat their defenders - midfielders - forwards and score a goal to kick your opponents out of the tournament.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Defeat your opponents by using attack cards to take out their players. With the action cards, you can bully your fellow players by, for example, taking their cards, having them skip a turn, stealing a player and even more 'nasty' bullying cards! Of course, you can also defend your players in this game with the defence cards (blocks the attack card) or the offside card (blocks the action card). There are also 'super cards' in the game, each of which has a special power. If you really quickly kick your opponent out of the tournament, throw up the 'Penalty' card to take out multiple players immediately. Each team also has a Coach and can be used against the most dangerous attacks to defend you from the other player's attempts to score a goal.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;&amp;mdash;description from the publisher&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Met MadSoccer breng je de spanning van het EK naar je woonkamer! MadSoccer geeft jou de kans met jouw team de rest van de andere teams te verslaan en zo de competitie te winnen.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;&amp;mdash;description from the publisher (Dutch)&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
